 all the killer film and video on this site!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Living life so fully, so passionately, has been a true gift.  I am one of the luckiest people on Earth to have discovered something so enormous, so inspiring, that it has changed the course of my life.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As a result, I live life on the fringe - outside the mainstream.  Whether it is my career as an independent artist or my deep passion for chasing eclipses, everything I do is unconventional.  The choices I have made in my life baffle my friends.  But I know who I am.  And I will go my own way no matter the cost.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I am heavily into music - cosmology - metaphysics - and art of all kinds.  I have gazillions of friends all over the world and value celebration, self-expression and community above all else.  Yup, I guess I am a bit of a bohemian.  When I am not chasing eclipses, playing guitar or reading, you can find me at Burning Man, at a yoga class or camping for the summer solstice.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"alignright\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/portrait.jpg\" alt=\"dm portrait\" /></p>','About Eclipseguy',0,'','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-31','','','2009-06-01 13:13:59','2009-06-01 17:13:59','',2,'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2-revision-31',0,'revision','',0),(1159,5,'2009-06-01 13:55:24','2009-06-01 17:55:24','<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tim_shot.jpg\" alt=\"dm photo\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I have been obsessed by Total Solar Eclipses (TSEs) ever since I saw my first one in Baja, Mexico, in 1991.  Since that day, I have chased eclipses of all kinds to every corner of the globe - from India to Brazil, Antarctica to Libya.  I am constantly planning wondrous and exotic adventures to stand in the shadow of the Moon and have a big desire to share th