n find me at Burning Man, at a yoga class or camping for the summer solstice.</p>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignright\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/portrait.jpg\" alt=\"dm portrait\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This website is my rant on the internet about how you - yes you, right there -Â  should see at least one Total Solar Eclipse before you die. To live your entire life and never realize the power and beauty of the universe in which you live is such a waste! Believe me - most people will settle for a mediocre, programmatic existence.Â  Don\'t be one of them!Â  Get pumped!Â  Life is so fleeting!Â  Quit waiting for someone to fire the starting gun!Â  Waking up to the truth about the universe, the world and yourself is the stuff life is made of.Â  But opening the eyes takes passion, curiosity and a willingness to take risks.Â  All things that are living inside of you already.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You are much more than you have been lead to believe.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So stick around.Â  Read the Trip Reports.Â  See the photos.Â  Watch the videos.Â  Get inspired and comment on anything you see.Â  You haveÂ  just stumbled across the hidden world of eclipse chasers.Â  And we want you to join us.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You must see a Total Solar Eclipse at least once before you die!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>','About Eclipseguy',0,'','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-36','','','2009-06-01 13:51:07','2009-06-01 17:51:07','',2,'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2-revision-36',0,'revision','',0),(1160,5,'2009-06-01 13:57:40','2009-06-01 17:57:40','<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tim_shot.jpg\" alt=\"dm photo\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I have been obsessed by Total Solar Eclipses (TSEs) ever