ence.Â  Don\'t be one of them!Â  Get pumped!Â  Life is so fleeting!Â  Waking up to the truth about the universe, the world and yourself is the stuff life is made of.Â  You need passion, curiosity and a willingness to take risks.Â  All things that are living inside of you already.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Remember: you are much more than you have been lead to believe.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Watch the videos.Â  Read the Trip Reports.Â  Get inspired and comment on anything you see.Â  You have just stumbled across the hidden world of eclipse chasers.Â  And we want you to join us - at least once!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You must see a Total Solar Eclipse before you die!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>','About Eclipseguy',0,'','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-46','','','2009-06-05 21:16:07','2009-06-06 01:16:07','',2,'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2-revision-46',0,'revision','',0),(1275,5,'2009-06-05 21:18:46','2009-06-06 01:18:46','<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tim_shot.jpg\" alt=\"dm photo\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I am fascinated with the universe. I have been obsessed by Total Solar Eclipses ever since 11 July 1991 - the day I first stood in the shadow of the Moon.Â  On that day I woke up to the reality that life is much more than it seems.Â  The eclipse forced me to break through the two-dimensional barrier known as the sky and peer into a deep, dynamic and powerful universeÂ  -  as much a part of me as I am of it.Â  It was oneness.Â  An epiphany, a breakthrough, a peak experience.Â  If life is a series of awakenings then this was a big one!Â  I haven\'t been the same since.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Not all eclipse chasers feel the same way.Â  But we have one thing in common:Â  we love solar eclipses.