9-revision-31',0,'revision','',0),(2387,5,'2012-05-23 14:00:45','2012-05-23 18:00:45','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/video/beads-in-arizona\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/annularity_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"news annularity 2012\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>While thousands of onlookers enjoyed the May 20 annular eclipse from places like the Grand Canyon and Zion National Park, a small team of us ventured to the eclipse path\'s southern limit in Arizona to try to catch a glimpse of the \"edge phenomenon\" that is only visible during this kind of eclipse.  And what a great idea it was!  <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/video/beads-in-arizona\">See the brand new documentary here</a>.</blockquote>','Success In The Desert!',0,'Spectacular annular eclipse bedazzles thousands in the American southwest May 20.  \r\nBrand New Documentary Film','publish','open','open','','success-in-the-desert','','http://eclipseguy.dev/video/beads-in-arizona\nhttp://eclipseguy.dev/video/beads-in-arizona','2012-06-30 23:29:04','2012-07-01 03:29:04','',0,'http://eclipseguy.dev/?p=2387',0,'post','',0),(2388,5,'2012-05-23 13:59:12','2012-05-23 17:59:12','<img src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/annularity_thumb.jpg\" alt=\"news annularity 2012\" />\n\nWhile thousands of onlookers enjoyed the May 20 annular eclipse from places like the Grand Canyon and Zion National Park, a small team of us ventured to the eclipse path\'s southern limit in Arizona to try to catch a glimpse of the\"edge phenomenon\" that is only visible during this kind of eclipse.  And what a great idea it was!  I have just returned home - working on the video right now.  Come back in a few days!','Success In The Desert!',0,'Spectacular annular eclipse bedazzles thousands in the American southwest May 20.  ','inherit','open','open','','2387-revision','','','2012-05-23 13:59:12','2012-05-23 17:59:12','',2387,'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/23