15','',2572,'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2572-autosave',0,'revision','',0),(2580,5,'2012-06-05 23:37:51','2012-06-06 03:37:51','During the eclipse expedition to China in 2008, we passed through the city of Xi\'an and had the chance to see the famous Terracotta Warriors. More than 8,000 warriors, horses and chariots have been uncovered.  They were created in 246 BC but not discovered until 1974. My invitation into the private area in the facility to film the warriors that are being repaired allowed me to get amazing, close up pictures of these sculptures.','The Terracotta Warriors',0,'The magnificent Terracotta Warriors!  Unique, behind-the-scenes footage - rarely seen like this. ','inherit','open','open','','958-revision-8','','','2012-06-05 23:37:51','2012-06-06 03:37:51','',958,'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/958-revision-8',0,'revision','',0),(2581,5,'2012-11-19 18:00:47','2012-11-19 22:00:47','<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We really earned this one!</h3>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/lakeland_totality_wide.jpg\" alt=\"wide video grab\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mid-totality on November 14, 2012 - from Lakeland, Australia</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/lakeland_diamond.jpg\" alt=\"diamond video grab\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Totality begins with a glorious Diamond Ring.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/video/australia-eclipse-raw-video\">HERE is the link to the New RAW VIDEO</a> from this eclipse.  Full Trip Report and new documentary film in the works ...','Eclipse Chasing in Australia',0,'TOTAL success in Queensland - November 14, 2012. \r\nNew RAW VIDEO posted!','publish','open','open','','eclipse-chasing-in-australia','','\nhttp://eclipseguy.dev/video/australia-eclipse-raw-vid