://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/IMG_3486A.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2948,5,'2012-11-19 18:10:49','2012-11-19 22:10:49','<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #ff9900;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Solar Eclipse Expeditions</span></span></h2>\r\nHere is the accounting of my adventures into the Moon\'s shadow over the last 22 years.  You get the date, the place, the eclipse type and duration observed. Available Trip Reports are linked in blue.\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\"><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">11 Jul 1991</span> </span>- <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/total-solar-eclipse-11-july-1991-mexico\">La Paz, Mexico</a> - Total - 6:50</h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">04 Jan 1992 </span>- Catalina Island, USA - Annular - not seen </strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">10 May 1994</span> - Stratford, Canada - Annular - </strong>5:39</h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">03 Nov 1994</span> - <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/brazil-03-november-1994\">Iguazu Falls, Brazil </a>- Total - 3:39</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">24 Oct 1995</span> - <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/india-24-october-1995\">Fatehpur Sikri, India </a>- Total -  0:59</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">26 Feb 1998</span> - <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/aruba-26-february-1998\">Baby Beach, Aruba</a> - Total -  3:34</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">11 Aug 1999 </span>- Hasankeyf, Turkey - Total - 2:09</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">31 Jul 2000</span> - <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/the-arctic-31-july-2000\">Pond Inlet, Canada</a> - Partial</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">25 Dec 2000 </span>- Toronto, Canada - Partial</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">21 Jun 2001</span> - <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/zambia-21-june-2001\">Lusaka, Zambia</a> - Total - 3:35</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">10 Jun 2002</span> - <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/puerto-vallarta-10-june-2002\">Puerta Vallarta, Mexico</a> - Annular - barely seen</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">04 Dec 2002</span> - <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/outback-02-december-2002\">Outback, Australia</a> - Total - 0:24</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">23 Nov 2003</span> - <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/antarctica-23-november-2003\">Antarctica</a> - Total - 1:14</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">29 Mar 2006 </span>- <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/libya-29-march-2006\">Jalu, Libya</a> - Total - 4:04</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">01 Aug 2008</span> - <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/china-01-august-2008\">Yiwu, China</a> - Total - 1:55</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">22 Jul 2009</span> - Moganshan, China - Total - 2:15</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">11 Jul 2010</span> - <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/tripreport/south-america-%E2%80%93-11-july-2010\">Calafate, Argentina</a> - Total - 2:40</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">20 May 2012</span> - <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/video/beads-in-arizona\">Arizona, USA</a> - Annular - 2:04</strong></h4>\r\n<h4><strong><span style=\"color: #ffcc99;\">13 Nov 2012</span> - Lakeland, Australia - Total - 1:28\r\n</strong></h4>\r\nWith such short durations, it is hard to imagine that in my life I have stood in the Moon\'s shadow for over 30 minutes!\r\n\r\nOn to the next one..!','22 Years of Expeditions',0,'Twenty-two years of eclipse chasing and all I got was this list on the internet!      ','inherit','open','open','','2089-revision-42','','','2012-11-19 18:10:49','2012-11-19 22:10:49','',2089,'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2089-revision-42',0,'revision','',0),(2949,5,'2015-03-24 13:52:08','2015-03-24 17:52:08','Here is the first look at our successful observation of the Total Solar Eclipse of March 20, 2015 from our Air Berlin 737 high above the North Sea.  We are all very happy!  This was an incredibly exciting chase and my first from the air.  My 21st eclipse!  Short film in the works!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote><a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web-600.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2922 aligncenter\" alt=\"tse 2015 web 600\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web-600.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"375\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The beginning of totality and the Diamond Ring.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web3-600.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2932 aligncenter\" alt=\"tse-2015-web3-600\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web3-600.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"375\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The stunning sight of the Moon\'s shadow sweeping down from space and crossing the Earth. Ice crystals on the window!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2933\" alt=\"tse-2015-web2-600\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web2-600.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mid-totality.</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">And watch the Moon\'s shadow race across the North Sea in this satellite animation ...</p>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://vine.co/v/OYAhHMbvjYp/embed/postcard\" height=\"600\" width=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://platform.vine.co/static/scripts/embed.js\"></script></blockquote>\r\n</blockquote>','Success at 37,000 ft. above the North Sea!',0,'Only days ago, eclipse flight out of Germany stuns chasers with never-before-seen views.  ','inherit','open','open','','2921-revision-10','','','2015-03-24 13:52:08','2015-03-24 17:52:08','',2921,'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2921-revision-10',0,'revision','',0),(2950,5,'2014-11-14 15:46:03','2014-11-14 19:46:03','&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" alt=\"pitchman biz card\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/pitchman_card_1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Since delivering my presentation at the Toronto TEDx Convention, I have been asked to speak at all kinds of meetings and on expeditions about our place in the universe - talking about what I have learned from two decades of eclipse chasing.  From this, my alter ego as \"The Pitchman For The Universe\" has taken shape.  Don\'t get me started!  In 2015, I am looking for opportunities to present my hour-long talk \"Partnering With The Universe.\"</p>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" alt=\"dave talks at TED\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/ted_talk_1.jpg\" />\r\n\r\nNuggets from the talk can be found under the \"Musings\" main navigation tab at the top of the page on this website.  You can view my TEDx video <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/video/my-presentation-at-tedx-toronto\" target=\"_self\">here</a> - view a primer video for my talk <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/22826936\" target=\"_blank\">here</a> - and download the flyer in pdf format <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/partnering_flyer2.pdf\">here</a>.\r\n\r\nTo inquire about booking The Pitchman For The Universe, leave a comment at the bottom of this page, or contact me <a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/contact\" target=\"_self\">here</a>.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" alt=\"dave talks at TED again\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/ted_talk_2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Partnering With The Universe</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For 20 years, David Makepeace has travelled the world to witness Total Solar Eclipses - a natural phenomenon that has been called the most spectacular event you can witness from Earth.</p>\r\n\"When the shadow of the Moon sweeps over us, we are brought into direct contact with a tangible presence that is awe-inspiring.  That there is a powerful relationship between us and the immense forces of the universe becomes undeniable.\"\r\n\r\nWhat possible relationship could you have to the universe?  How could it make a difference in your life?\r\n\r\nWith breathtaking film and video captured around the world at eclipse events, Makepeace takes us on a tour of our world and our solar system - widening the perspective on our lives as only an eclipse chaser can.  Discover how the simple beauty and mystery of our world can open the door to a greater awareness of what we are and our place in the universe.','Speaking Engagements',0,'The Pitchman For The Universe is on tour in 2014.  Come see my inspiring presentation about our place in the universe.','inherit','open','open','','2261-revision-49','','','2014-11-14 15:46:03','2014-11-14 19:46:03','',2261,'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2261-revision-49',0,'revision','',0),(2951,5,'2015-03-24 16:29:03','2015-03-24 20:29:03','&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" alt=\"pitchman biz card\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/pitchman_card_1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Since delivering my presentation at the Toronto TEDx Convention, I have been asked to speak at all kinds of meetings and on expeditions about our place in the universe - talking about what I have learned from two decades of eclipse chasing.  From this, my alter ego as \"The Pitchman For The Universe\" has taken shape.  Don\'t get me started!  In 2015, I am looking for opportunities to present my hour-long talk \"Partnering With The Universe.\"</p>\r\n<img cl