 21st eclipse!  Short film in the works!\r\n<a href=\"http://nordlandseite.de/berichte/reise/sonnenfinsternis2015.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Here</a> is a another cool article about our flight - great pics - in German, but Google Translate works well enough.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/TSE_2015_GROUP_PHOTO_600.jpeg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2953 aligncenter\" alt=\"TSE_2015_GROUP_PHOTO_600\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/TSE_2015_GROUP_PHOTO_600.jpeg\" width=\"600\" height=\"235\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote><a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web-600.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2922 aligncenter\" alt=\"tse 2015 web 600\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web-600.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"375\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The beginning of totality and the Diamond Ring.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web3-600.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2932 aligncenter\" alt=\"tse-2015-web3-600\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web3-600.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"375\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The stunning sight of the Moon\'s shadow sweeping down from space and crossing the Earth.\r\nIce crystals on the window!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2933\" alt=\"tse-2015-web2-600\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web2-600.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mid-totality.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/Malicki_totality_2015.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-2955 aligncenter\" alt=\"Malicki_totality_2015\" src=\"http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/Malicki_totality_2015.jpg\" width=\"630\" height=\"419\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">